snippet.title: Headbangers Rhythm Royale - Announcement Trailer - Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
Headbangers Rhythm Royale is coming to Nintendo Switch on October 31, 2023! Wishlist today: https://www.nintendo.com/store/products/headbangers-rhythm-royale-switch/

Headbangers Rhythm Royale is a rhythm-based, party game, battle royale mix full of music-focused multiplayer mini-games. Up to 30 pigeons battle it out to become the master headbanger.

#Headbangers #NintendoSwitch #NintendoDirect
